sentences: Born in Louisiana, she currently resides in New York City.
In 2014, DJ Kiss joined Oprah Winfrey on her 8-city "The Life That You Want" Tour.
DJ Kiss frequently appears Good Morning America as the Special Guest DJ.
She was also featured as the music correspondent on VH1's Big Morning Buzz and MTV's “The Seven”."
In 2016, DJ Kiss, along with her husband DJ M.O.S., deejayed the 88th Academy Awards Governors Ball.
